Cherubim and Seraphim Church, The King of Glory, Obawole, Lagos, has scheduled November 29th to December 8th, 2018 for its 2018 Mountain of Covenant Programme, tagged “My Year of Testimony.” A statement signed by the Church Spiritual mother, Prophetess Idowu Sanyaolu JP, reveals that the 2018 Mountain of Covenant is meant to free believers from spiritual bondage, especially as the year is going to an end. The programme, which will hold at the church auditorium in Lagos, will feature healing, breakthrough, salvation and deliverance. Important guests and notable men and women of God are expected to grace the annual programme.